items.title: 5 people dead in crash on Highway 83, 2 injured
items.description: A total of five people were killed in a car crash on Highway 83 in Douglas County. Three of those people were children.

items.title: Dog a "CPR Hero" for helping save owner's life during cardiac arrest
items.description: A couple say Polly the golden retriever was so "in tune" with her owner, she helped save his life when his heart stopped in the middle of the night.

items.title: Trump proposal to exclude nursing as a professional degree sparks outcry
items.description: Nursing advocates say a proposed rule could worsen a shortage of professionals in the field and lead to worse health outcomes.
